readable.content: A dancer in a dancing pose on the street , audience in the backgound . A female performer is barefoot and performing in front of a crowd . A woman in a tank top and capri pants costume taking a bow in the street . A woman with beads around her neck is performing a dance as part of a parade . Female street entertainer with horns doing a curtsey .
